{"title":"Bruxismo iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología/Bruxismo iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Bruxismo","guid":"ENxVxpKqE57-qTJdysg6-A","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición y\\NClasificación","guid":"-GnUaqmF47hzr6QWIRWlTg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"BRUXISMO = actividad muscular mandibular repetitiva durante sueño o vigilia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Consenso Internacional 2013 → no es trastorno sino comportamiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"SEGÚN\\NMOMENTO","guid":"R6uRTa7iePxy1gjifohRgA","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Bruxismo del\\Nsueño (BS)","guid":"-BoexpXgbjCko5cz22Na6g","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"Ocurre durante NREM → arousal asociado","guid":"9XMGmFQHVGoib-i25IwdjA","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"EMG → ritmo masticatorio (RMMA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"El paciente NO es consciente → difícil diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"4","text":"Bruxismo de\\Nvigilia (BV)","guid":"GyfbB3LVeFhTuRL9fEGitw","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Apretamiento dental consciente o semiconsciente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Asociado a tensión emocional, concentración","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"GRADO DIAGNÓSTICO\\N(Consenso 2013)","guid":"2Dgrxd0wL2mR88upRLzRrw","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"Posible → autoreporte o reporte familiar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"Probable → reporte + hallazgos clínicos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"Definitivo → confirmación polisomnográfica","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"Prevalencia general 8-31% (varía por método diagnóstico)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"BS pediátrico 5-50% → autolimitado en mayoría","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"Adultos → BS ~13%, BV ~20%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"16","text":"MAYOR prevalencia en mujer joven con estrés","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"0","text":"Fisiopatología","guid":"","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"MULTIFACTORIAL → interacción central + periférica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"Sistema\\Nnervioso central","guid":"qsT7HzSAWe_iqA7h2ZX0gg","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"DOPAMINA → rol principal","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"↓ dopamina → ↑ actividad muscular masticatoria","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"23","text":"Serotonina → modulación sueño-bruxismo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"23","text":"Noradrenalina → arousal relacionado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"21","text":"Rol del arousal\\Nen sueño","guid":"J5Tndi9os79tgrLfV-0vFw","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Microdespertares → preceden RMMA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"Activación SNA simpático → ↑ FC → luego RMMA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"BS fuertemente asociado a transiciones de etapas NREM","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"21","text":"Músculo masetero\\Ne hipertrofia","guid":"jxFbY3QJ5V3AWexDDcWGNg","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"Hipertrofia masetero → signo cardinal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"Fatiga matutina muscular → BS","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"21","text":"HIPÓTESIS MYRHAUG\\N(histórica)","guid":"U4HYP3hK4HCuY1bmUdCC7w","children":[{"id":"36","parent":"35","text":"Espasmo muscular → reflejo tensor del velo palatino","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"35","text":"→ disfunción trompa de Eustaquio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"35","text":"EVIDENCIA ACTUAL → no confirmada por EMG (Penkner et al.)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"Factores\\Nde Riesgo","guid":"n0WlNlc3IUxfODKAtzSOZw","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"Psicológicos →\\NMAYOR peso","guid":"TKWhFi2xZqWpwJ7yrP5DLw","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Estrés psicosocial → factor precipitante #1","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Ansiedad → OR elevado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"Trastornos del sueño concurrentes","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"39","text":"Neurológicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"Parkinson → bruxismo prevalente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"TCE","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"39","text":"Fármacos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"ISRS → ↑ bruxismo por efecto serotonérgico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"Antipsicóticos (haloperidol, metoclopramida) → vía dopaminérgica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"Anfetaminas, cocaína","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"Inhibidores de la recaptación de serotonina-noradrenalina","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"39","text":"Sistémicos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Apnea obstructiva del sueño → comorbilidad frecuente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"Reflujo gastroesofágico","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"39","text":"Oclusales → ROL DISCUTIDO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"Maloclusión → ya no considerada causa principal","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"0","text":"Manifestaciones\\NClínicas","guid":"2o8xHfmy2QKk91-SECv0Vg","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"Orofaciales","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Desgaste dental → facetas de desgaste","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Hipertrofia masetero bilateral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"58","text":"Dolor muscular masticatorio matutino","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"58","text":"Trismus o limitación apertura mandibular","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"58","text":"Cefalea tensional temporal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"58","text":"Dolor ATM → crujidos, chasquido","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"57","text":"SÍNTOMAS OTOLÓGICOS →\\NMUY FRECUENTES","guid":"buAnhu_wV1WnvO_n8vO8YA","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Otalgia → mecanismo referido via V par craneal (auriculotemporal)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"Sensación de oído tapado (fullness)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"Tinnitus","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"Mareos / vértigo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"65","text":"Hipoacusia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"65","text":"Evidencia → TMD moderado-severo → otalgia OR significativo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"57","text":"Hallazgos en\\Ntimpanometría","guid":"QAahw3p42o-UI0pbArt_kQ","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Curva As (plana con\\Nreflejos conservados)","guid":"jOQYThFLKG_iQIiZqno7RQ","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"Diferencial → otosclerosis vs DTM-bruxismo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"TC alta resolución → distingue otosclerosis de variante DTM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"PERLA: reflejos conservados apuntan contra otosclerosis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"72","text":"Conexión fosa mandibular-oído medio → caso reportado","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico","guid":"","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"GOLD STANDARD → polisomnografía + audio/video","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"En práctica clínica → probable o posible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"Evaluación\\Nclínica","guid":"9Y6n9QUE_N4CcxKlqPThrQ","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"Palpar masetero → hipertrofia y dolor","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"Evaluar desgaste dental","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"Explorar ATM → apertura, crujidos, desviación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"81","text":"Escala Fonseca (FAI) → severidad DTM","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"78","text":"Estudios\\Ncomplementarios","guid":"uxUBaee1cE8modZY3j_8Hw","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Audiometría + timpanometría","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"TC ATM de alta resolución → si curva As sin explicación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"RMN ATM → desplazamiento discal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"86","text":"PSG → confirmación definitiva BS","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"78","text":"Criterios\\NICSD-3\\N(BS)","guid":"6Al4RiehAt_HTprDsG4YSA","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Rechinamiento nocturno >=3 noches/semana x >=3 meses","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"+ al menos uno: desgaste, dolor muscular matutino, cefalea temporal, trismus al despertar","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"94","parent":"0","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"95","parent":"94","text":"ENFOQUE MULTIDISCIPLINARIO OBLIGATORIO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"94","text":"Equipos: ORL + Odontología/DTM + Kinesiología + Psicología","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"94","text":"NO FARMACOLÓGICO\\N(PRIMERA LÍNEA)","guid":"ELZ2cQdIdSyKKkiYMYCNbw","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Férula\\Noclusal","guid":"s5ECW59Avz7l4lGkw2g-kg","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"Férula dura → ESTÁNDAR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"↓ actividad RMMA nocturna, protege dientes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"98","text":"MEJORA calidad de sueño (meta-análisis 2024)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"98","text":"No cura el bruxismo → reduce consecuencias","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"97","text":"Fisioterapia y\\Nterapia manual","guid":"4Dak1fRFdcgT-dOGM3dVOw","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Terapia manual cervical + ejercicios mandibulares → ↓ tinnitus, otalgia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"Terapia miofuncional orofacial → mejora otalgia y fullness","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"97","text":"Biofeedback","guid":"","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"Dispositivos portátiles → detectan EMG masetero nocturno","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"106","text":"Retroalimentación → interrumpe episodio de bruxismo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"97","text":"Higiene\\Ndel sueño","guid":"Cy0xGyzpnPvlV28qIiP4YQ","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"Rutina bedtime relajada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"↓ estimulación mental previa al sueño","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"Considerar evaluación SAHOS concurrente","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"97","text":"Manejo del estrés","guid":"","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"Terapia cognitivo-conductual → evidencia creciente","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"94","text":"FARMACOLÓGICO\\N(SEGUNDA LÍNEA)","guid":"n78D6F60meiYeIhnxr8FTw","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"Toxina botulínica\\Ntipo A (BTX-A)","guid":"iBTqvnEXmWgaODjfWY7kBA","children":[{"id":"117","parent":"116","text":"Inyección bilateral masetero ± temporal ± pterigoideo medial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"116","text":"↓ actividad EMG + ↓ dolor (VAS)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"116","text":"Meta-análisis 2025 → efectivo, pero heterogeneidad de estudios","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"116","text":"Efecto temporal → requiere repetición c/3-6 meses","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"115","text":"Clonazepam → uso nocturno, evidencia limitada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"115","text":"Levodopa → casos con Parkinson","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"115","text":"EVITAR benzodiazepinas de forma crónica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"115","text":"Suspender ISRS si sospecha causal → coordinar psiquiatría","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"Curva As con reflejos conservados → pensar en DTM antes que otosclerosis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"Otalgia sin patología ótica primaria → siempre explorar ATM y masetero","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"Bruxismo inducido por ISRS → frecuente y subdiagnosticado → PREGUNTAR fármacos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"Terapia manual cervical + ejercicios mandibulares reduce síntomas otológicos del DTM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"125","text":"No existe tratamiento único universal → enfoque multidisciplinario siempre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"125","text":"BTX-A efectiva para reducir actividad muscular → no reemplaza férula oclusal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"125","text":"Desgaste dental + hipertrofia masetero + cefalea matutina = tríada diagnóstica BS","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"0","text":"VER TAMBIÉN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"→ ORL_Neurofisio_Examen (ORL)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"→ Vestibular Schwannoma (Neurootología)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"1. Assiri HA et al. Bruxism treatment outcomes: A systematic review and meta-analysis. Medicine (Baltimore). 2025;104(49):e46247. DOI: 10.1097/MD.0000000000046247","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"2. Yacoub S et al. Efficacy of botulinum toxin type A in bruxism management. Dent Med Probl. 2025;62(1):145-160. DOI: 10.17219/dmp/186553","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"3. Ferreira GF et al. Effect of occlusal appliances on the sleep of individuals with bruxism. Cranio. 2024;44(1):59-70. DOI: 10.1080/08869634.2024.2444712","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"136","text":"4. Tavares LF et al. Effectiveness of manual therapy and exercise therapy on otological symptoms of TMD. Disabil Rehabil. 2024;47(15):3794-3808. DOI: 10.1080/09638288.2024.2435525","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"136","text":"5. Yap AU et al. Association of TMD severity with otologic symptoms in Asian youths. Cranio. 2022;43(1):128-134. DOI: 10.1080/08869634.2022.2088455","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"136","text":"6. Penkner K et al. Function of tensor veli palatini in TMD patients with aural symptoms. J Oral Rehabil. 2000;27(4):344-8. DOI: 10.1046/j.1365-2842.2000.00530.x","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"136","text":"7. Hidaka H et al. Transient hearing loss and tinnitus induced by mouth opening: TMJ-middle ear connection. Otol Neurotol. 2016;37(7):e217-21. DOI: 10.1097/MAO.0000000000001078","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":143,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"ORL","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología","filename":"Bruxismo iPad","id":"map_1559","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Bruxismo iPad"}